# UI/UX

## Rules

- Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Responsive: use Tailwind breakpoints
- Tailwking custom colors
- Loading/error states required
- 44x44px minimum touch targets

## Components

```typescript
import { Button } from "@/components/Button";
import { Badge } from "@/components/Badge";

export function UserCard({ user }: { user: User }) {
  return (
    <div className="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-bg-primary border border-border-primary rounded-lg">
      <Badge variant="secondary">{user.status}</Badge>
      <Button size="sm">Action</Button>
    </div>
  );
}
```

## Color Tokens

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Semantic tokens
className="bg-bg-primary text-text-primary border-border-primary"

// ❌ BAD: Raw Tailwind colors
className="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 border-gray-200"
```

## Loading States

```typescript
const query = useQuery();

if (query.isLoading) return <LoadingSpinner />;
if (query.error) return <ErrorMessage error={query.error} />;
return <ResourceList data={query.data} />;
```
